  "body": "### Description\n\nExtension for SmallRye Ractive Messaging Kafka depends on vertx-kafka-client whereas the former doesn't have that dependency anymore.\r\n\r\nThe dependency is currently there solely for configuring a couple of serde classes for Vert.x types such as JsonObject, JsonArray and Buffer.\r\n\r\nIn addition, vertx-kafka-client depends on the 2.6.0 version of kafka-clients, which is no more compatible with the latest version (3.0.0 at the time). The transitive dependency exclusion is in place but it causes some confusion : #22000, https://github.com/kiegroup/kogito-examples/pull/1022\r\n\r\n\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nRemoving this would be a breaking change as we'll remove the mentioned serde classes completely or at least \"provide\" them inside the Quarkus extension with a different package name.\r\n",
